1
00:00:35,966 --> 00:00:38,633
=Angels and Guards=

2
00:00:38,633 --> 00:00:41,233
=Episode 21=

3
00:00:42,500 --> 00:00:43,166
What?

4
00:00:44,166 --> 00:00:46,200
They killed my Black and White Reapers

5
00:00:46,500 --> 00:00:47,733
and wiped out my advance force?

6
00:00:48,433 --> 00:00:49,666
I will tear them

7
00:00:50,500 --> 00:00:51,866
to pieces.

8
00:00:52,900 --> 00:00:53,500
Go.

9
00:00:57,800 --> 00:01:01,066
(Yunnan Border)

10
00:01:11,733 --> 00:01:12,400
By tomorrow morning,

11
00:01:12,833 --> 00:01:14,100
Tuba Zangxi's assassins

12
00:01:14,233 --> 00:01:15,433
will surround Liangjie.

13
00:01:16,700 --> 00:01:17,800
This time, we have no backup.

14
00:01:18,166 --> 00:01:19,500
We are truly on our own.

15
00:01:21,066 --> 00:01:21,566
Our mission

16
00:01:21,566 --> 00:01:23,433
is to escort Prince Yuanrong
to the border.

17
00:01:24,266 --> 00:01:25,300
Everything else

18
00:01:26,700 --> 00:01:28,366
can wait until the mission is done.

19
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:29,800
So,

20
00:01:30,533 --> 00:01:32,533
we stand together and fight
through them.

21
00:01:32,933 --> 00:01:35,366
We get Fa Yuanrong safely to the border.

22
00:02:26,566 --> 00:02:27,066
Get them!

23
00:03:18,500 --> 00:03:19,733
I'm warning you. I'm about to strike.

24
00:03:24,166 --> 00:03:25,333
I really mean it.

25
00:03:36,200 --> 00:03:38,233
Young people, don't be so rash.

26
00:03:38,833 --> 00:03:39,666
Rashness is bad.

27
00:03:40,166 --> 00:03:41,500
Can't you take advice?

28
00:03:44,666 --> 00:03:45,233
Stop!

29
00:03:47,066 --> 00:03:49,566
Ganging up on one man is not heroic.

30
00:03:49,666 --> 00:03:51,733
I still have my ultimate move.

31
00:04:08,133 --> 00:04:09,200
(Heroes, spare me!)

32
00:04:09,666 --> 00:04:10,733
Heroes, spare me!

33
00:04:11,266 --> 00:04:12,166
Heroes, spare me!

34
00:04:12,200 --> 00:04:13,466
I have an old mother at home

35
00:04:13,500 --> 00:04:14,833
and a two-year-old child.

36
00:04:15,066 --> 00:04:16,166
You can't kill me!

37
00:04:16,200 --> 00:04:16,933
Heroes, spare me!

38
00:04:16,933 --> 00:04:17,533
Spare me!

39
00:04:17,866 --> 00:04:19,033
You can't kill me!

40
00:04:19,500 --> 00:04:20,366
Please!

41
00:04:20,500 --> 00:04:21,533
Spare me!

42
00:04:21,766 --> 00:04:22,800
Spare me!

43
00:04:23,066 --> 00:04:23,633
Stop!

44
00:04:50,700 --> 00:04:51,700
"Heroes, spare me."

45
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:53,066
I know.

46
00:04:59,400 --> 00:05:01,266
Young Master Chang, what do we do now?

47
00:05:01,900 --> 00:05:02,733
Since you have decided

48
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:04,333
to escort Fa Yuanrong to the border,

49
00:05:04,766 --> 00:05:05,833
we can't delay.

50
00:05:06,533 --> 00:05:07,800
We take him to the border river.

51
00:05:08,066 --> 00:05:08,666
Once he is there,

52
00:05:09,100 --> 00:05:10,466
our mission is over.

53
00:05:11,066 --> 00:05:12,733
The rest will be up to him.

54
00:05:13,366 --> 00:05:14,266
There is no time to lose.

55
00:05:14,566 --> 00:05:15,500
Let's go.

56
00:05:42,266 --> 00:05:42,800
Strange.

57
00:05:43,566 --> 00:05:46,400
Why is no one here
to welcome the prince home?

58
00:05:47,233 --> 00:05:48,000
It seems

59
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:49,700
it is over.

60
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:51,600
Young Duke,

61
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:53,300
what do you mean?

62
00:05:53,900 --> 00:05:54,666
Forgive my bluntness.

63
00:05:55,700 --> 00:05:56,533
As things stand,

64
00:05:59,266 --> 00:06:00,700
you are a discarded pawn.

65
00:06:02,233 --> 00:06:02,833
What does that mean?

66
00:06:04,166 --> 00:06:04,900
It means

67
00:06:05,166 --> 00:06:06,833
the court has recognized
Liao's new regime.

68
00:06:07,533 --> 00:06:08,566
He no longer serves a purpose.

69
00:06:10,566 --> 00:06:11,100
But when

70
00:06:11,500 --> 00:06:13,200
we escorted Prince Yuanrong
out of the capital,

71
00:06:13,200 --> 00:06:14,133
that was not the situation.

72
00:06:15,100 --> 00:06:15,866
Court policy

73
00:06:16,533 --> 00:06:17,900
can change in an instant.

74
00:06:18,900 --> 00:06:20,133
My source is certain.

75
00:06:21,233 --> 00:06:22,933
The court and Liao's new King

76
00:06:24,166 --> 00:06:25,533
have already formed an alliance.

77
00:06:28,166 --> 00:06:29,166
How could this happen?

78
00:06:30,500 --> 00:06:31,766
The mighty Ming Empire...

79
00:06:32,533 --> 00:06:33,600
Why would it lie to me?

80
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:36,900
Things change.

81
00:06:37,933 --> 00:06:39,333
This is no time for grief or anger.

82
00:06:39,766 --> 00:06:41,200
You need to decide

83
00:06:42,033 --> 00:06:42,966
your next move quickly.

84
00:06:44,333 --> 00:06:46,266
Yuanrong, you have to stay strong

85
00:06:46,900 --> 00:06:48,066
and think about what comes next.

86
00:06:50,833 --> 00:06:52,033
I only want to go home.

87
00:06:53,700 --> 00:06:54,600
My home

88
00:06:55,666 --> 00:06:56,666
is right across that river.

89
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,233
Please, think clearly.

90
00:06:59,400 --> 00:07:00,966
This is not the time to fall apart.

91
00:07:04,400 --> 00:07:04,666
No.

92
00:07:05,433 --> 00:07:05,833
Yuanrong.

93
00:07:05,866 --> 00:07:06,466
I'm going home.

94
00:07:07,266 --> 00:07:08,366
I have to go home.

95
00:07:09,566 --> 00:07:10,600
No matter what happens,

96
00:07:11,400 --> 00:07:12,500
even if I lose my head,

97
00:07:13,333 --> 00:07:14,333
even if arrows pierce my heart,

98
00:07:14,766 --> 00:07:15,766
even if my enemies kill me,

99
00:07:16,533 --> 00:07:17,733
I still have to go home.

100
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:19,333
Yuanrong.

101
00:07:21,433 --> 00:07:21,933
Xintian.

102
00:07:22,900 --> 00:07:23,833
If you take another step,

103
00:07:24,366 --> 00:07:25,433
you will be in Liao.

104
00:07:25,700 --> 00:07:27,766
Crossing the border
without permission is treason.

105
00:07:28,200 --> 00:07:29,200
That is a capital crime.

106
00:07:39,266 --> 00:07:41,200
(Order from the Commander
of the Northern Bureau.)

107
00:07:41,566 --> 00:07:42,733
Shen Bingfan,

108
00:07:42,733 --> 00:07:45,400
Hua Mange, and Cheng Xintian

109
00:07:45,566 --> 00:07:47,500
are to escort Fa Yuanrong
back to the capital at once.

110
00:07:48,566 --> 00:07:49,566
The Commander

111
00:07:50,033 --> 00:07:51,933
ordered us to escort
Prince Yuanrong back.

112
00:07:53,866 --> 00:07:54,933
It seems Zhang Weimin

113
00:07:55,366 --> 00:07:56,600
has persuaded the Cabinet.

114
00:07:56,866 --> 00:07:58,733
(Liao's new King, Fa Gao,)

115
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:00,200
(seized the throne through rebellion.)

116
00:08:00,266 --> 00:08:01,466
(His regime is still unstable.)

117
00:08:01,733 --> 00:08:04,133
(To gain greater support from Ming,)

118
00:08:04,700 --> 00:08:05,200
(he will surely)

119
00:08:05,666 --> 00:08:09,166
(make many promises to His Majesty
and the Cabinet.)

120
00:08:09,433 --> 00:08:10,600
(Fa Gao)

121
00:08:10,666 --> 00:08:11,700
(is quite bold,)

122
00:08:11,900 --> 00:08:13,433
(but he is also ambitious.)

123
00:08:13,833 --> 00:08:16,666
(Once his throne is secure,)

124
00:08:17,533 --> 00:08:18,800
(he may well turn against us.)

125
00:08:19,200 --> 00:08:21,300
(Keep Fa Yuanrong alive for now.)

126
00:08:21,566 --> 00:08:23,966
(If Fa Gao betrays us one day,)

127
00:08:24,433 --> 00:08:27,166
(Fa Yuanrong will
be our bargaining chip.)

128
00:08:27,833 --> 00:08:28,866
So that means

129
00:08:29,366 --> 00:08:30,900
Prince Yuanrong does not have to die.

130
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:32,533
You could say that.

131
00:08:33,033 --> 00:08:35,433
But once he returns to the capital,
he will still be confined.

132
00:08:36,666 --> 00:08:38,433
Yuanrong, did you hear that?

133
00:08:38,500 --> 00:08:39,500
You don't have to die.

134
00:08:39,833 --> 00:08:41,233
This is the best outcome we could get.

135
00:08:41,900 --> 00:08:43,233
I hope you can endure this humiliation

136
00:08:44,500 --> 00:08:45,400
and wait for your chance.

137
00:08:48,900 --> 00:08:49,666
Yuanrong.

138
00:08:53,033 --> 00:08:54,133
Everyone went through so much
because of me.

139
00:08:54,866 --> 00:08:55,766
I dragged you all into this.

140
00:08:56,866 --> 00:08:58,200
I'm deeply ashamed.

141
00:09:35,266 --> 00:09:35,866
Yuanrong.

142
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:48,966
Yuanrong.

143
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:49,600
Yuanrong, wake up.

144
00:09:49,600 --> 00:09:51,033
Yuanrong, don't scare me.

145
00:09:51,933 --> 00:09:52,700
Yuanrong.

146
00:10:08,666 --> 00:10:09,233
I...

147
00:10:11,233 --> 00:10:12,733
I could not outrun fate after all.

148
00:10:13,333 --> 00:10:14,666
Here by the river near Liangjie...

149
00:10:15,166 --> 00:10:16,500
This is where I die.

150
00:10:17,066 --> 00:10:18,000
Yuanrong.

151
00:10:23,500 --> 00:10:24,833
Yuanrong, stop talking.

152
00:10:25,233 --> 00:10:26,266
You will be fine.

153
00:10:27,700 --> 00:10:29,133
I only wanted to go home.

154
00:10:30,866 --> 00:10:32,366
Why would they not let me go home?

155
00:10:33,766 --> 00:10:35,366
I never wanted to be the King.

156
00:10:38,700 --> 00:10:39,466
Xintian.

157
00:10:40,733 --> 00:10:42,966
I only wanted a simple life with you.

158
00:10:43,333 --> 00:10:44,166
Why

159
00:10:44,833 --> 00:10:46,100
couldn't I even have that?

160
00:10:48,066 --> 00:10:48,600
Yuanrong.

161
00:10:53,233 --> 00:10:54,133
In my next life,

162
00:10:55,500 --> 00:10:57,200
may I never be born into a royal house.

163
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:12,866
Home.

164
00:11:13,266 --> 00:11:13,966
Home.

165
00:11:18,400 --> 00:11:19,333
Home.

166
00:11:21,266 --> 00:11:22,266
Home.

167
00:11:23,900 --> 00:11:25,466
Home.

168
00:11:31,766 --> 00:11:32,500
Yuanrong.

169
00:11:42,200 --> 00:11:43,466
Yuanrong.

170
00:11:45,700 --> 00:11:47,200
Yuanrong.

171
00:11:48,666 --> 00:11:49,733
Yuanrong.

172
00:12:00,166 --> 00:12:01,666
Leng Xin got away again.

173
00:12:02,533 --> 00:12:03,400
Bingfan was

174
00:12:03,766 --> 00:12:04,766
overwhelmed by shock and rage.

175
00:12:25,733 --> 00:12:26,766
Leave us for now.

176
00:12:56,033 --> 00:12:56,566
Father.

177
00:12:57,533 --> 00:12:58,200
Mother.

178
00:12:59,033 --> 00:12:59,866
Run.

179
00:13:00,566 --> 00:13:01,900
Leng Xin is here.

180
00:13:03,933 --> 00:13:04,600
Beiming.

181
00:13:06,066 --> 00:13:06,766
Hurry.

182
00:13:07,166 --> 00:13:08,400
Help me catch Leng Xin.

183
00:13:16,766 --> 00:13:17,333
Bingfan.

184
00:13:19,066 --> 00:13:20,466
Leng Xin appeared again.

185
00:13:22,400 --> 00:13:23,566
And I failed to catch him again.

186
00:13:24,066 --> 00:13:25,933
He escaped right in front of me.

187
00:13:27,500 --> 00:13:28,166
Beiming.

188
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:30,466
I'm so useless.

189
00:13:32,500 --> 00:13:33,033
Bingfan.

190
00:13:34,500 --> 00:13:36,233
I will help you catch Leng Xin.

191
00:13:40,266 --> 00:13:41,033
Really?

192
00:13:42,600 --> 00:13:43,300
Really.

193
00:13:44,866 --> 00:13:46,866
I have been watching
that villain for a long time.

194
00:13:47,766 --> 00:13:50,333
Now that he has dared to kill
in front of me,

195
00:13:51,933 --> 00:13:53,200
I will catch him

196
00:13:54,533 --> 00:13:55,600
and make him pay.

197
00:14:19,666 --> 00:14:22,200
This trip to Yunnan and Guizhou
was full of danger.

198
00:14:23,100 --> 00:14:24,300
No one knows what awaits us

199
00:14:24,400 --> 00:14:25,666
when we return to the capital.

200
00:14:26,666 --> 00:14:28,533
But now that Leng Xin has appeared,

201
00:14:29,666 --> 00:14:31,533
it means we are getting closer
to the truth.

202
00:14:32,033 --> 00:14:32,966
Are you afraid?

203
00:14:35,266 --> 00:14:36,166
No.

204
00:14:37,766 --> 00:14:38,766
If fear could stop me,

205
00:14:40,066 --> 00:14:41,833
it would have stopped me
seven years ago.

206
00:14:44,166 --> 00:14:46,100
Leng Xin, that murderous demon...

207
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:49,266
I will catch him.

208
00:14:50,566 --> 00:14:52,500
I will catch him.

209
00:14:56,900 --> 00:14:58,133
I will help you catch him.

210
00:14:59,900 --> 00:15:00,800
As long as I'm here,

211
00:15:02,833 --> 00:15:04,700
I will not let him hurt you again.

212
00:15:28,666 --> 00:15:29,366
Xintian is asleep.

213
00:15:30,766 --> 00:15:31,366
What about you?

214
00:15:31,700 --> 00:15:32,366
Are you hurt?

215
00:15:34,033 --> 00:15:35,200
I'm the lucky one, remember?

216
00:15:35,500 --> 00:15:36,433
How could I get hurt?

217
00:15:37,266 --> 00:15:38,033
Duoyu.

218
00:15:38,900 --> 00:15:39,966
Honestly,

219
00:15:40,566 --> 00:15:42,233
having you around is kind of reassuring.

220
00:15:43,333 --> 00:15:44,100
I told you

221
00:15:44,666 --> 00:15:46,266
I would protect you well.

222
00:15:50,766 --> 00:15:51,433
Do you

223
00:15:52,000 --> 00:15:53,266
have a grudge against Leng Xin?

224
00:15:58,400 --> 00:15:59,066
No.

225
00:15:59,500 --> 00:16:00,066
Hua,

226
00:16:00,433 --> 00:16:01,666
why ask that all of a sudden?

227
00:16:03,200 --> 00:16:03,800
Duoyu.

228
00:16:04,833 --> 00:16:05,666
Actually,

229
00:16:06,233 --> 00:16:07,433
if there is anything

230
00:16:08,033 --> 00:16:09,133
on your mind, you can tell me.

231
00:16:13,166 --> 00:16:13,933
Seven years ago,

232
00:16:14,533 --> 00:16:15,533
in Prince Luo's treason case,

233
00:16:16,666 --> 00:16:19,100
the key witness was Xu Wenchang.

234
00:16:21,000 --> 00:16:22,566
Are tou a descendant of the Xu family?

235
00:16:28,166 --> 00:16:29,066
That is why

236
00:16:29,066 --> 00:16:30,333
I had to join the Northern Bureau.

237
00:16:33,666 --> 00:16:35,600
But no matter how many times
I begged the Commander,

238
00:16:36,700 --> 00:16:38,133
he refused to let me in.

239
00:16:38,866 --> 00:16:39,733
Maybe

240
00:16:41,066 --> 00:16:42,466
he was trying to protect you.

241
00:16:43,566 --> 00:16:44,300
Maybe

242
00:16:45,233 --> 00:16:46,800
he was afraid I would uncover the truth.

243
00:16:47,766 --> 00:16:48,533
Duoyu.

244
00:16:49,266 --> 00:16:51,633
If we meet Leng Xin again,
don't act rashly.

245
00:16:51,933 --> 00:16:52,933
You have us.

246
00:16:53,566 --> 00:16:54,633
We will face him together.

247
00:16:55,933 --> 00:16:56,933
Don't worry, Hua.

248
00:16:58,366 --> 00:16:59,433
It has been seven years.

249
00:17:00,000 --> 00:17:00,933
I will not act rashly.

250
00:17:01,600 --> 00:17:03,200
I will catch him with my own hands.

251
00:17:11,800 --> 00:17:14,666
(In Memory of Fa Yuanrong)

252
00:17:17,900 --> 00:17:18,433
Xintian.

253
00:17:18,566 --> 00:17:19,000
Let's go.

254
00:17:19,566 --> 00:17:20,333
Bingfan.

255
00:17:21,333 --> 00:17:22,433
I want to stay

256
00:17:22,900 --> 00:17:23,933
with Yuanrong.

257
00:17:25,600 --> 00:17:26,800
We'll arrest Leng Xin together,

258
00:17:27,066 --> 00:17:28,100
find the one behind all this,

259
00:17:28,166 --> 00:17:29,200
and avenge Yuanrong.

260
00:17:29,733 --> 00:17:30,833
Right. Xintian.

261
00:17:31,366 --> 00:17:32,700
We will uncover the truth together.

262
00:17:33,100 --> 00:17:33,933
We can't let Yuanrong

263
00:17:33,933 --> 00:17:35,366
die without answers.

264
00:17:37,833 --> 00:17:38,400
All right.

265
00:18:01,900 --> 00:18:05,133
By the Mandate of Heaven,
the Emperor decrees:

266
00:18:05,433 --> 00:18:07,000
Li Qingshan, Governor of Yunnan,

267
00:18:07,266 --> 00:18:10,600
has impeached Baihu Shen Bingfan
of the Jinyiwei Northern Bureau.

268
00:18:11,166 --> 00:18:12,600
At the border relay station,

269
00:18:12,600 --> 00:18:13,800
she acted with arrogance,

270
00:18:13,833 --> 00:18:15,000
defied the law,

271
00:18:15,366 --> 00:18:17,900
and unlawfully killed soldiers
under the Governor's Office.

272
00:18:18,100 --> 00:18:20,833
(Li Qingshan, Governor of Yunnan)
This is treason, an unforgivable crime.

273
00:18:21,233 --> 00:18:22,333
(Imperial Edict)
Upon receipt of this edict,

274
00:18:22,366 --> 00:18:24,766
(Imperial Edict)
they shall be dismissed, arrested,

275
00:18:24,900 --> 00:18:26,500
and sent to the Imperial Prison
for trial.

276
00:18:26,733 --> 00:18:27,933
By imperial command.

277
00:18:28,200 --> 00:18:29,533
Yes.

278
00:18:45,866 --> 00:18:49,033
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

279
00:18:49,400 --> 00:18:52,766
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

280
00:18:53,033 --> 00:18:56,033
♪My heart drifted lost♪

281
00:18:56,033 --> 00:18:59,433
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

282
00:19:00,533 --> 00:19:03,733
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

283
00:19:04,166 --> 00:19:07,500
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

284
00:19:08,100 --> 00:19:10,300
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

285
00:19:10,300 --> 00:19:14,333
♪I've softly let it go♪

286
00:19:14,333 --> 00:19:18,200
♪The vow you made was true♪

287
00:19:18,200 --> 00:19:21,933
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

288
00:19:22,266 --> 00:19:24,166
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

289
00:19:24,166 --> 00:19:28,700
♪And forget at world's end♪

290
00:19:29,000 --> 00:19:30,500
♪Embracing memory♪

291
00:19:30,500 --> 00:19:32,866
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

292
00:19:32,866 --> 00:19:36,733
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

293
00:19:36,766 --> 00:19:39,066
♪I wish to let it pass♪

294
00:19:39,100 --> 00:19:44,100
♪And run toward this vast life♪
